<bibRefCitation id="D11A2CAAED34FFB6FBD1F825FA88F805" author="Wang, C. &amp; Li, S. Q." box="[1090,1290,1939,1965]" pageId="38" pageNumber="189" pagination="43 - 69" refId="ref13394" refString="Wang, C. &amp; Li, S. Q. (2020) Seven new species of jumping spiders (Araneae, Salticidae) from Xishuangbanna, China. ZooKeys, 968, 43 - 69. https: // doi. org / 10.3897 / zookeys. 968.55047" type="journal article" year="2020">Wang &amp; Li 2020</bibRefCitation>
; Wang, pers. comm.). We also collected this species from tree trunks in 
